{"type": "article", "id": 2228, "title": "可充电水壶 KettleCharge", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T23:11:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222257fUhSw2t5RpWrI14V.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">户外旅行时，除了移动充电器，还有什么可以满足你随时充电的需要？或许你可以尝试一下 BioLite 推出的这款全新可充电水壶 KettleCharge，它在具备一般水壶都具有的烧水功能之外，还可以通过 USB 为电子设备提供充电功能,通过内置于底部的热传导发电装置，将烧水产生的热能转化为电能。KettleCharge 适用于包括火炉、电磁炉在内的任何加热装置，所以不失为一款野外旅行必备品。为了使得你的电子设备与热源保持安全距离，它还配有一条耐热的USB延长线。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t目前 KettleCharge 的售价定为 149.95 美元，<a href=\"http://biolitestove.com/products/kettlecharge/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135116TfqrzvPFDhCm5QVN.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"320\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135117HcxWN2KBaI9SOgs6.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5628866\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135117YP8oAHt0WQZ4sDNO.png\" width=\"640\" height=\"422\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65974026\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}